Danzig - Skeletons 2015 320ak

Skeletons is the tenth studio album by Danzig,(excluding the 2007 double-disc Lost Tracks compilation of B-sides and outtakes), released on November 27, 2015. Skeletons is an album of cover songs ranging from Elvis Presley to Black Sabbath. The album's first single, originally released online in 2012 and played live since, is the theme from the biker film of the same name, "Devil's Angels".
